name: Enroute Ladies' Insulated Jacket
description:
The Enroute combines a heat-reflective lining, zip off hood and soft touch storm cuffs with an elegant silhouette, accented by an adjustable waist belt.  Looking stylish in any environment, the Enroute will keep you warm on the coldest of days.

100% textured polyester
8,000 mm waterproofness

name: Ladies' Double Up Stretch Soft Shell
description:
The double weave construction provides an updated, technical look.  Two way stretch for comfort and fit.  Water resistant finish to keep you dry.  Articulated elbows and adjustable cuffs.

92/8 nylon/spandex double weave

name: Skyline Ladies' Twill Jacket
description: A roll-away hood and a stylish storm flap with upper snaps provide elegance to a jacket that can handle the rugged.  A midweight jacket with waterproofness makes this great for around town.

name: Women's Lux Down Coat
description:
Rated all the way to -32F.  
Zip-off thermal hood with shock cord
Insulated side inserts and lower sleeve panels.
Stretch storm cuffs
Waterproof zippers

70% down, 30% feathers.

Model shown 5'7", coat size S

name: Escape Ladies Bonded Fleece
description:
An awesome bonded fleece, at 7.4oz it will keep you warm.  The zipper garages and sleeve inserts utilize the "fleece" side for a texture variance.  A hidden kiss zipper on the chest provides an easy place to place small valuables while on your pursuit.

100% bonded polyester jersey

name: Women's Performance Stretch
description:
Extended Sleeves with thumb gaiter
100% poly interlock bonded to 100% poly
Internal Audio port access
Our most popular women's jacket!

Contrast side panels, inner collar, sleeves and shoulders provide detail.  Chainstitching on the sleeve inserts sets off the look.  Articulated sleeves add comfort and mobility and the shaped side panels provide a feminine cut.

name: Uptown Men's Urban Jacket
description:
Comfortable uptown or going down mountain, this 3 layer light bonded jacket features style to have you looking good anywhere, while keeping you warm and comfortable.  

Inside placket with stylized storm flap and square metal snap at
top and rivet at bottom
Right chest pocket with shaped zipper garage
Soft touch rib inner collar and storm cuffs with adjustable tabs and
metal snaps
Center front zipper with metal zipper pulls
Square metal rivet details on front and back armhole
Pocket flaps with side entry zippered pockets
Audio port access through inside left pocket

100% polyester two-tone textured bonded
8000mm waterproof

name: Kali Burnout Thermal
description:
Kali - a Goddess embodying the fierce aspect of the Devine.  Simple in design, yet super in function.  From epic to errand is so applicable.  There's very little you can't do in the Kali long sleeve.  Be fierce, be Devine.

60/40 cotton/poly

name: Butter Midweight Hoodie
description:
The Butter hoodie gets it's name from it's feel, buttery.  Soft and supple waffle construction, brand tag centered on the hood and a simple sleeve stamp.  Around town, as a layer on the mountain, or a cool Spring morning, it's perfect.

60/40 cotton/poly.

name: Solitude Stretch V
description:
The Solitude V provides longer length and a stretchy feel in a slimmer fit silhouette.   Great for your daily endless pursuit.  

pre-shrunk 98% ring spun cotton, 2% spandex

name: The All Day Pant
description:
The ultimate lounge pant, the All Day pants are ready for just that, all day. Breakfast, kids to school, yoga session, coffee, and home.  Roomy, wide legs and a wide waistband with drawstring ties. Made of soft Eco-Heather for a retro heather look with sustainable appeal. The lime print pops.  Embellished with Right quad stamp and center rear waistband "endless pursuit."

Sustainable eco-heather cotton

name: Womens Session l/s Layer
description:
The balance of a little more edge while keeping it subtle.  We took the success of the men's Session design and carried it over to a 2-for-1 deal for the women.  Roughed edge t-shirt with a stitched in long sleeve layer.  Athletic fit with some sweet style.

100% combed ring-spun cotton for ultimate softness.

name: Unresticted Stretch Weather Zip
description: Stylish design with contrast panels specifically placed to engineer unrestricted movement, allowing you to swing freely and not be bound by your apparel.  Inside storm placket with chin guard.  Two front pockets with garage zippers.  Adjustable cuffs with tabs.  Adjustable shock cord at waist.  Constructed of a wind barrier fabric and laminated with water resistance.  This jacket is here to disrupt the golf layer world!

name: Barcode Ultimate Polo
description: Simply the best polo we make.  Performance stretch fabric features a tonal barcode pattern.  Raglan style sleeves with stretch insert panels from the under arm to the front shoulder provide unrestricted movement.  The fabric feels like a second skin and is always cool.  Our modern fit with a 3 button placket and diagonal stitch.  Antimicrobial, moisture wicking and UV 40 built right in.

name: Maze Emobssed Polo
description:
Performance stretch embossed print.  3 button placket with diagonal lower stitching.  Straight bottom hem with side slits for a better fit.  Moisture wicking, antimicrobial and UV protection built right in.

89/11 polyester/spandex

name: Impact Pique Polo
description: One button placket combined with asymmetrical stripes for a very current tour-style look.  Moisture wicking, antimicrobial and UV protection make this an awesome and versatile polo.

name: Accelerate Performance Polo
description:
The cool-logik panels sewn into the center-back, sleeves and sides are made from a unique cooling yarn integrated into the fabric, providing a cooling factor in all the right places.  Contrasting inner placket matches the front and back shoulder inserts.  Moisture wicking, antimicrobial and our modern stretch fit make this a versatile favorite from the 1st hole to the 19th.

91/9 poly/spandex
inserts:  moisture wicking 100% poly jacquard with cooling

54/46 recycled poly/wicking poly

name: Symmetry Performance Polo
description: The Symmetry polo features our new coffee deodorizing performance, along with standard moisture wicking, antimicrobial and UV protection properties.  The two-tone interlock construction gives cool detail to the body.

name: Refresh Perfomance Melange Polo
description:
A raglan style sleeve for easier movement.  Mesh contrasting side panels and lower sleeves provide added durability.  Contrast piping and insert panel along the back shoulder blades and lats provides a more tailored fit.  Coffee deodorizing, moisture wicking, antimicrobial and UV protection all built in.

100% polyester melange

name: Stride Argyle Polo
description:

100% polyester diamond jacquard

name: Launch Classic Polo
description: Classic stripe polo, the "country club" look if you will.  Made of new snag protection fabrics so you don't get the pick.  Moisture wicking, antimicrobial and UV protection.

name: 1/4 Zip Wind and Rain Jacket
description: The Teflon coating provides water resistance, while the sanded poly microfiber provides an excellent wind break.  Elastic shockcord at the waist, stand up collar, velcro security closure pockets and noiseless fabrication make this an excellent addition to any golf bag.

name: Polyester Pinstripe 1/2 Zip
description:
Contoured forward shoulder seams and tonal cover stitch bring an updated look to the classic pullover.  Moisture wicking and anitmicrobial construction.  Perfect for that 8am tee time or cool jog. 

100% polyester mini pinstripe with mesh backing.

name: Shifty Hoodie
description: Dark grey bonded fleece.  Provides mad warmth and comfort with a load of features.  Removable draw string hood, thumb gators, and inner media pocket with audio cable grommet and neck loop to keep you buds from flapping around.  Stamp icon on the left sleeve and a brand label on the hood.

name: Decent Thermal
description:
The Decent thermal provides warmth and wicking all day long, whether as a layer on a Heli day or wearing out on a brisk morning for coffee.  Year round style, all day comfort.  Ready for any pursuit.

Abyss Grey.

name: Base Beanie

name: Newsboy Hat
